OL,3,CDad named locally as one of men who
OL,4,Cdied trying to rescue children from sea
OL,6,FA man who died trying to rescue
OL,7,Fchildren from the sea off the coast at
OL,8,FHartlepool has been named locally as
OL,9,Fdad Wayne Taylor.
OL,11,FCleveland Police said officers were
OL,12,Fcalled at around 3.45pm on Sunday (12
OL,13,FJuly) after concerns were raised for
OL,14,Ftwo children who had got into
OL,15,Fdifficulty in the water at Seaton
OL,16,FCarew beach.
OL,18,FTwo men entered the sea to assist the
OL,19,Fchildren, who were taken to hospital
OL,20,Fto be checked over as a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
