FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784182683
OL,3,CDad named locally as one of men who
OL,4,Cdied trying to rescue children from sea
OL,6,FRNLI staff brought the men out of the
OL,7,Fwater and they received immediate
OL,8,Fmedical treatment, but died a short
OL,9,Ftime later.
OL,11,FTributes have been paid online to Mr
OL,12,FTaylor, who has been named locally as
OL,13,Fone of the men to have lost their
OL,14,Flives.
OL,16,FCleveland Police said two other men
OL,17,Fentered the water to assist in the
OL,18,Frescue effort, but both managed to get
OL,19,Fout of the water safely.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
