CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784182683
OL,3,CDad named locally as one of men who
OL,4,Cdied trying to rescue children from sea
OL,6,FDavey Short said he was one of those
OL,7,Fmen.
OL,9,FHe told ITV Tyne Tees: "I just wanted
OL,10,Fto get out there to help the little
OL,11,Fboy what was screaming 'help'. I just
OL,12,Ftold him to swim towards me, 'keep
OL,13,Fswimming towards us'. I managed to get
OL,14,Fto him and got him out."
OL,16,FDescribed on social media as a "hero",
OL,17,FMr Short rejected the label and said
OL,18,Fhe would do it again.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
