OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784182683
OL,3,CDad named locally as one of men who
OL,4,Cdied trying to rescue children from sea
OL,6,F"I'm no hero, I just did what any man
OL,7,Fwould do - or any dad," he added. "And
OL,8,FI would do it again today if I had to."
OL,10,FCleveland Police have said formal
OL,11,Fidentification is yet to take place
OL,12,Ffor the men.
OL,14,FThe force is also urging people to
OL,15,Fseek out and adhere to safety advice.
OL,17,FFind sea safety information here,
OL,18,Fbeach safety information here and
OL,19,Fadvice for what to do if you fall in
OL,20,Fthe water here.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/4
